260
00:18:07,700 --> 00:18:11,500
Did you tell Celeste about
your dinner date with Aurelia?

261
00:18:11,567 --> 00:18:13,367
It's not a date.

262
00:18:13,433 --> 00:18:15,667
I was supposed to tell her

263
00:18:15,733 --> 00:18:18,333
but she sounded so stressed
in Sorsogon.

264
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:21,300
I don't want to add
to her worries.

265
00:18:21,400 --> 00:18:24,100
Are you sure
that's the better option?

266
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:26,800
Yes.

267
00:18:26,867 --> 00:18:27,967
I'm just warning you.

268
00:18:29,300 --> 00:18:30,967
This could blow up in your face.

269
00:18:31,033 --> 00:18:34,233
What could possibly go wrong
with one dinner?

270
00:18:34,300 --> 00:18:37,533
As long as I'm sure about
what I feel about Celeste,

271
00:18:37,600 --> 00:18:39,367
I don't see any problem.

272
00:18:51,400 --> 00:18:52,933
Really?

273
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:59,233
Did Hazel offer to promote
Celeste's pili business?

274
00:18:59,333 --> 00:19:03,633
That's so unbelievable.

275
00:19:03,700 --> 00:19:06,667
Ouch.

276
00:19:06,733 --> 00:19:09,067
Hazel is like that ever since.

277
00:19:09,133 --> 00:19:12,733
She wants Sorsogon to be known
in the whole world.

278
00:19:12,800 --> 00:19:14,200
Put it on the map.

279
00:19:14,267 --> 00:19:18,533
Just like me of course
to help the community.

280
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:21,000
Really, Mikoy?

281
00:19:21,067 --> 00:19:25,033
Why? Is there any
possible reason?

282
00:19:25,100 --> 00:19:27,467
It's not that I have doubts,

283
00:19:27,533 --> 00:19:33,433
but my point is her intention
is doubtful.

284
00:19:33,533 --> 00:19:37,533
You know Hazel is not like that.

285
00:19:37,600 --> 00:19:40,033
I know her better than you do.

286
00:19:40,100 --> 00:19:42,700
Hey Mikoy,
between the two of us,

287
00:19:42,767 --> 00:19:44,033
I'm the woman.

288
00:19:44,100 --> 00:19:45,633
So I know better.

289
00:19:45,700 --> 00:19:47,000
You should listen to me.

290
00:19:47,067 --> 00:19:49,167
So what do you think
about Hazel?

291
00:19:49,233 --> 00:19:50,867
What do you think
is her intention,

292
00:19:50,933 --> 00:19:55,667
why she's helping Celeste's
family with their business?

293
00:19:55,733 --> 00:19:59,733
What else but to study Celeste.

294
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:05,967
Check the competition.

295
00:20:07,600 --> 00:20:14,800
Plus, she's doing that just
to make sure there's no chance

296
00:20:14,867 --> 00:20:19,733
for Mikoy to fall in love.

297
00:20:22,800 --> 00:20:25,300
As they say...

298
00:20:25,367 --> 00:20:30,933
wait, check, check, one,
two, three, there you go.

299
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:36,700
Keep your friends close,
your enemies closer,

300
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:41,267
and your rival in love,
the closest.

301
00:20:41,333 --> 00:20:48,367
So when the chance comes
you can easily crush the enemy.

302
00:20:48,433 --> 00:20:50,967
And I thank you!

303
00:20:53,633 --> 00:20:56,767
May, what you're thinking is
wrong.

304
00:20:56,833 --> 00:20:59,167
Hazel is not that kind of woman.

305
00:20:59,233 --> 00:21:03,233
She's not the type of woman
who is insecure.

306
00:21:03,300 --> 00:21:05,533
Unlike you.

307
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:06,867
Why me?

308
00:21:21,667 --> 00:21:23,900
Mr. Ben, Mr. Nanding?

309
00:21:23,967 --> 00:21:26,067
Sebastian, where is James?

310
00:21:28,633 --> 00:21:32,833
James had a personal emergency.

311
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:35,967
So it's just me and Basti
who are here.

312
00:21:36,033 --> 00:21:39,133
I noticed lately that
he often looks at my girlfriend.

313
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:41,233
So I asked him to stay away.

314
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:43,733
You are really something,
Sebastian.

315
00:21:43,833 --> 00:21:46,467
You really want to be alone
with Tiffany, right?

316
00:21:46,533 --> 00:21:50,333
That's why I'm very thrilled
with this...

317
00:21:50,400 --> 00:21:52,533
with my sweetheart.

318
00:21:54,667 --> 00:21:58,433
Anyway, I'm so excited to show
the locals how your community

319
00:21:58,500 --> 00:22:03,100
will be the next go-to place
in the Philippines.

320
00:22:28,533 --> 00:22:29,900
Here, Mr. Ben.

321
00:22:29,967 --> 00:22:31,333
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

322
00:22:39,633 --> 00:22:40,667
Do you want some?

323
00:23:21,767 --> 00:23:23,667
Are the people here like this?

324
00:23:23,733 --> 00:23:26,567
I prepared for this presentation
but they didn't show up.

325
00:23:26,633 --> 00:23:27,600
Tiff...

326
00:23:29,033 --> 00:23:31,033
you just have
to be patient with them.

327
00:23:31,100 --> 00:23:32,100
Patient?

328
00:23:32,167 --> 00:23:33,967
Really, Basti?

329
00:23:34,033 --> 00:23:36,100
I waited there the whole day.

330
00:23:36,167 --> 00:23:38,933
My eyes already turned white but
not even one of them showed up.

331
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:41,400
Tiffany, if that is
your attitude

332
00:23:41,467 --> 00:23:44,133
then it's justified
if no one came here.

333
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:46,533
You thought you are the center
of the universe.

334
00:23:46,600 --> 00:23:47,933
Who are you?

335
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:50,367
You think highly of yourself.

336
00:23:50,433 --> 00:23:51,733
Take back what you said.

337
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:53,000
Why should I take it back?

338
00:23:53,067 --> 00:23:54,333
That's the truth.

339
00:23:58,700 --> 00:24:01,333
Of course, I'm insecure.

340
00:24:01,400 --> 00:24:05,467
I mean, I should be.

341
00:24:05,533 --> 00:24:11,200
Celeste is Mikoy's
the one who got away.

342
00:24:11,267 --> 00:24:13,167
Aren't you overreacting?

343
00:24:13,233 --> 00:24:14,867
You already won, right?

344
00:24:14,933 --> 00:24:17,167
You have Mikoy.

345
00:24:17,233 --> 00:24:18,767
I heard that woman
is getting married

346
00:24:18,833 --> 00:24:20,967
to a Chinese business tycoon.

347
00:24:21,033 --> 00:24:23,700
Friend, we never celebrate
a victory

348
00:24:23,767 --> 00:24:26,067
until the fat lady sings.

349
00:24:26,133 --> 00:24:28,167
And besides what?

350
00:24:28,233 --> 00:24:30,133
Just because she's here
in Sorsogon

351
00:24:30,233 --> 00:24:33,867
and she's getting married,
I should be complacent?

352
00:24:33,933 --> 00:24:38,633
My God, besides if that's
the case, why is she here?

353
00:24:38,700 --> 00:24:41,200
What if she's having
second thoughts?

354
00:24:41,267 --> 00:24:44,000
Oh my God, what if she calls off
the wedding?

355
00:24:44,067 --> 00:24:45,633
Oh my God.

356
00:24:45,700 --> 00:24:48,367
I knew it. Just one look
at that woman,

357
00:24:48,433 --> 00:24:50,633
I know I can't trust her.

358
00:24:50,700 --> 00:24:55,733
I can see right through her
and I know she's not sincere.

359
00:24:58,000 --> 00:25:04,433
That woman can single-handedly
ruin my happily ever after.

360
00:25:04,533 --> 00:25:08,300
If that's the case,
what will you do?

361
00:25:08,367 --> 00:25:11,767
I won't let her ruin my plans.

362
00:25:11,833 --> 00:25:16,467
I will show her
that Mikoy is just mine.

363
00:25:16,533 --> 00:25:19,267
And if she ever makes a move
on Mikoy,

364
00:25:19,333 --> 00:25:22,400
I swear I will tear her down.

365
00:25:22,467 --> 00:25:24,567
I don't care about her.

366
00:25:24,633 --> 00:25:26,433
I don't care about her family.

367
00:25:26,500 --> 00:25:31,167
I will crush her finely,
just like a pili nut.

368
00:26:03,767 --> 00:26:04,933
What are you doing here?

369
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:06,833
You did something to me, right?

370
00:26:06,900 --> 00:26:10,900
Welcome, partners
and welcome to the future.

371
00:26:11,000 --> 00:26:13,267
Let's go here.

372
00:26:13,333 --> 00:26:14,533
She looks like a dog.

373
00:26:14,600 --> 00:26:16,967
If you keep on suppressing
what you truly feel.

374
00:26:17,033 --> 00:26:19,233
It might come out of your chest.

375
00:26:19,300 --> 00:26:21,433
It's up to you.
It might swell and bursts

376
00:26:21,500 --> 00:26:23,333
and becomes ruptured
appendicitis.

377
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:25,400
That's dangerous, Mikoy.

378
00:26:25,467 --> 00:26:27,800
She is the grandmother
respected by all.

379
00:26:27,867 --> 00:26:29,100
If you get her trust,

380
00:26:29,167 --> 00:26:31,200
you can get the trust
of the whole community.

381
00:26:31,267 --> 00:26:33,733
It's my pleasure
to meet you.

382
00:26:33,800 --> 00:26:34,967
Are you mad at me?

383
00:26:35,033 --> 00:26:37,133
No. Why would you say that?

384
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:40,867
It's obvious that whatever I do,
you will not like it.

385
00:26:40,933 --> 00:26:43,833
So it's my fault that
my standards are high.

386
00:26:43,933 --> 00:26:46,800
And you can't live up
to those standards?

387
00:26:46,867 --> 00:26:48,533
To a life without regret!

388
00:26:48,600 --> 00:26:50,333
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

389
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:52,433
I was unfair to her
because of you.

390
00:26:52,500 --> 00:26:53,667
Huh?

391
00:26:53,733 --> 00:26:55,667
Wait. What is my fault?

392
00:26:55,733 --> 00:26:57,167
You don't know...

393
00:26:57,233 --> 00:26:58,733
what you did to me?

394
00:27:00,500 --> 00:27:01,800
So what is this I feel?

395
00:27:01,867 --> 00:27:03,200
Imagination?
